text: This text appears to be a list of download links and magnets for the TV series "American Fiction (Season 5)" in various video qualities and formats. The links include those for Baidu Netdisk, Xunlei Cloud Disk, AliyanDisk, and BitTorrent magnet links. Each link or magnet is labeled with its size and resolution information. Some links have multiple resolutions available. At the end of the text, there's an invitation to scan a QR code or search for the public account "影的后花园" on WeChat to follow it.
